# Project Rules

1. Never use emojis in code, comments, or UI text.
2. Never create .md or .sql files. Use MCP tools for database migrations and keep documentation inline or in existing files.
3. All UI changes should be made while keeping the site's general UI in mind (dark/light theme support, Poppins font, existing spacing/border/color patterns, sidebar layout conventions).
